com.ge.dspmicro.commandhandler.machine.api

Enum MachineCommandType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MachineCommandType>
      • com.ge.dspmicro.commandhandler.machine.api.MachineCommandType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MachineCommandType>

    public enum MachineCommandType
extends Enum<MachineCommandType>
    Enum for the Type of commands Predix Machine can process. Below is an example way to call a command provided by the machine command handler. Note: you don't want to use the enum but the string value or this would create a bundle dependency on commandhandler.machine for the value. 
     // inject this from ther service registry.
      private ICommandDispatcher               dispatcher;
      
                  
      Map<String, String> payloadMap = new HashMap<>();
      payloadMap.put(ICommandDispatcher.COMMAND_KEY, "restart");
      ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
      String commandPayload = mapper.writeValueAsString(payloadMap);
      
      Map<String, String> commandMap = new HashMap<>();
      commandMap.put(ICommandDispatcher.COMMAND_HANDLER_TYPE_KEY, "Machine");
      commandMap.put(ICommandDispatcher.COMMAND_KEY, commandPayload);
      
      String restartCommand = mapper.writeValueAsString(commandMap);
      
      this.dispatcher.dispatchCommand(restartCommand);
